<template>
    {{ message }}
</template>

<script>
import {onMounted} from 'vue'
import Global from '@/Global';
export default {
    name: 'HomePage',
    setup() {
        const message = ref('No estas logeado');
        const url = Global.url;
        onMounted(async () =>{
            await fetch(url+'user',{
                headers: {'Content-Type': 'application/json'},
                credentials: 'include'
            })
        })

        return {
            message
        }
    }
}
</script>
